00:00:04.181 --> 00:00:06.225
when I change one of the numbers.

00:00:06.225 --> 00:00:08.035
And so let's look at this example.

00:00:08.035 --> 00:00:11.101
A group of four friends likes to bowl together,

00:00:11.101 --> 00:00:15.186
