00:01:49.854 --> 00:01:51.669
So my question is,

00:01:51.669 --> 00:01:54.549
well, the first question is, does this change the median?

00:01:55.519 --> 00:01:57.609
Well, remember the median is the middle number.

00:01:57.609 --> 00:02:00.163
And if we're looking at four numbers here,

00:02:00.163 --> 00:02:01.859
the median is going to be the average

00:02:01.859 --> 00:02:03.623
of the middle two numbers.

00:02:03.623 --> 00:02:04.668
So we're gonna take the average

00:02:04.668 --> 00:02:08.662
of whatever this question mark is and 220.

00:02:08.662 --> 00:02:12.238
That's going to be the median.

00:02:12.238 --> 00:02:15.396
Now, over here, after Adam has scored a new high score,

00:02:15.396 --> 00:02:17.137
